        <tr><td>Multi-location chain (hotel group, restaurant group)</td><td>Volume-discount quote</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Suppression installation / recharge / UL-300 cert</td><td>Suppression contractor scope (we don't do)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty</td><td>90 days parts and labor on hood-side work</td></tr>
